## Description ##
The pipeline is currently running `make scalapkg` twice when both Scala and Clojure API docs are required. This removes this duplication, and should save some time in CI.

## Checklist ##
- [x] Changes are complete (i.e. I finished coding on this PR)

### Changes ###
* Removed the `make scalapkg` and `make scalainstall` calls from the `build_scala_docs` and `build_clojure_docs` functions
* Moved this logic to a `build_scala` function that will trigger if either document set is expected

